title: WoW 3.3.5a Custom MoP Files
description:
These are custom files/patches to install in your 3.3.5a private WoW server to add many MoP files including DisplayIDs, Mounts, Weapons, Armor, Item, Companions, etc. All credit goes to kronixusa of Ac-Web. Contained in the file is a readme with links to videos and forums to walkthroughs on how to install these patches. If you have any questions about this content please ask kronixusa on Ac-Web Forums. 

I'm only uploading this torrent for faster download speeds. All permissions were given to me to do so.
